        Changes de default output
        
        + Default: `json`

        + Members
            + `json`
            + `conf`
            + `alter_system`
    + log_format (enum[string],optional)

        Changes de default log format
        
        + Default: `stderr`

        + Members
            + `stderr`
            + `csvlog`
            + `syslog`

